  "stemHtml": "<p>Bernoulli's equation is: <br>(Note: rho is density; P<strong><sub>STAT</sub></strong> is static pressure; P<strong><sub>DYN</sub></strong> is dynamic pressure; P<strong><sub>TOT</sub></strong> is total pressure)</p>",
  "options": {
    "a": "<p>P<sub>STAT</sub> + &frac12;rho &times; IAS<sup>2</sup> = constant</p>\r\n",
    "b": "<p>P<sub>STAT</sub> + &frac12;rho &times; TAS<sup>2</sup> = constant</p>\r\n",
    "c": "<p>P<sub>DYN</sub> + &frac12;rho &times; IAS<sup>2</sup> = constant</p>\r\n",
    "d": "<p>P<sub>TOT</sub> + &frac12;rho &times; TAS<sup>2</sup> = constant</p>\r\n"
